Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they got that out fast. They're really into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But not as much as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.49,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1B201D&\blur2.5\fs80\fnCartoon\b1\pos(640,118)\org(646,76)\frx350\fry0}Global Action Club
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fukube. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad. I can't let Juumoji get away with them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all here pretty early. You seem pretty fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If these would-be detectives are still standing around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that means the theft hasn't been committed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, Juumoji, if you're gonna strike then now's the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{op}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:11.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(233,200}Today is a real mess, but I get over it with a sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You get the idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:17.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:21.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You act as if nothing happened
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.64,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As if your heart didn't ache
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:28.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It almost feels encouraging,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}the way you're rushing me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hold it and let it overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:37.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We're all imperfect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't see it well in the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:46.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)}but if we can change our future selves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up and run
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:53.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go and surpass the mirage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Try to change and run
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}with the discomfort of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}We can reach that shining light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:07.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow it into the present
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't hesitate to act
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:15.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Deep or quick, just keep breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:20.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fs35\c&H283D2E&\frz3.45\pos(760,138)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.91,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(781,313)\blur3\bord1\clip(586,554,603,650)\t(-500,950,\clip(586,554,1280,650))\t(3826,4090,\clip(1280,554,1280,650))\3c&H29192B&\pos(1047,556)}The Final Target
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the last day! The most crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've met her somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Using the Juumoji incident to help sell {\i0}Hyouka{\i1} wasn't a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that won't be enough to sell them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I consider the alternatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dunno if it'll all work out though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Juumoji's next target is the Quiz Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no... What would he steal from them now that the main event's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've had enough too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong, Juumoji? Is the mysterious thief afraid of a crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard Juumoji faked us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Faked us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the Quiz Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Light Music Club.{keion}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They had some strings stolen.{gen}{or squid tentacles, according to doki}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Light Music Club? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, check for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the Light Music Club got hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Juumoji is far more flexible than I could have anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conventional methods won't cut it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must rethink my strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How else can I catch him, if not red-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.38,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H171B1A&\blur0.8\fnCartoon\b1\frz5.164\pos(605,105)}Target: {\c&H1E2526&}Sell all 2OO copies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.38,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H384348&\fs45\blur0.7\pos(604,266)\fnwhatever it takes\b1\frz2.856\frx10\fry2}82 sold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When it sells, it sells well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The twenty copies that Chitanda gave to Irisu sold out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so today she took another ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've sold another nine in total since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes for the rest of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Saturday all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving energy as usual, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! You really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful your big sister came all the way to check up on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? It's not your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm carrying out my own {\i1}One Red Paperclip{\i0} trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That pen turned into this mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You bartered your way up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dead at Dusk{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to kill some time with this, but it all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anshin'in Takuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"How did you like {\i1}Dead at Dusk{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels weird to say this myself, but I think it turned out pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I only helped with the backgrounds and hardly did anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you enjoyed it, that's thanks to the author and illustrator."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Anshin'in Takuha was a team name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not all of us are members of the Manga Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply share a fondness for manga, and as we talked, our ideas fit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to write our own manga, and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's not half bad for a first try, but we shouldn't praise ourselves too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll let you, the readers, be the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to split up after just one project, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already started on our next project for next year's Kan'ya Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to change the genre completely and do a mystery story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're thinking of giving a famous Christie novel a few twists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already decided on the title, so without further ado:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The title of our next project will be "Kudryavka's Order".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, another grim-sounding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us meet again at next year's Kan'ya Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anshin'in Takuha."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kudryavka's Order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who or what Kudryavka is, but the word "order" is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And "a famous Christie novel"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You might be able to kill some time with this, but it all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis, I sure hope you didn't bring something that's gonna cause even more trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.71,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fnArial Rounded MT\fs40\c&H4B6164&\frz0.8209\pos(680,182)}Radio Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Yoshino, the president of the Radio Club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm the Classics Club's president, Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the president of the Classics Club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect! I was just going to look for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join us as our guest for our lunchtime show?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be awesome to promote you as the president of Juumoji's final target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't even have to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be very happy to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you at twelve in the radio room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The show starts at twelve-thirty! Thanks in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we doing? Has anything happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They skipped "ku" and stole some strings from the Light Music Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to rethink our approach from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally engrossed in some indie manga. He's been like that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen this picture somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be your imagination. My sister just gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda, we don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much to bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me another page too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like the poster in front of the meeting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.52,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\bord0\blur1\p1\c&HC9D5DA&}m 811 193 l 817 314 l 761 312 l 746 183 m 62 262 l 69 454 l 225 456 l 195 252 
