Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.52,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1E262C&\blur0.55\fnFranklin Gothic Book\fs40\b1\pos(117,276)}to forget\Neverything\Nthat \Nhappened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, please let me borrow this manga for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to compare them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but bring it back soon! I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and change the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Ibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's okay... It was khaki in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so it won't be too apparent... I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, president. Please take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take off the Rainbow Parakeet costume.{she's mariko senri from the series}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweats?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not mine, it's Oreki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his sister gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this manga, Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ano desu ne}You know the culture fair poster, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{watashi}I can't stop thinking about how the same person must have drawn both that poster and this manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's this poster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of the meeting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.98,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\pos(273,193)}When light and dark are in balance.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.47,eyecatch big,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,641)\blur1.5\pos(640,62)}Autumn Equinox
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.47,eyecatch big,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,641)\bord0\blur1.5\pos(640,62)\t(1446,1670,\blur5)}Autumn Equinox
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\fad(777,0)\blur5\c&H000000&\b1\t(0,400,\blur1)\pos(640,54)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 99% sure it's the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the ears are drawn match perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a great weight's been lifted off my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we find out who drew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Tanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,From the Classics Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble, but do you know who drew that poster over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was Kugayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Kugayama Muneyoshi, the student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We pestered him to draw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not half bad, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I know both the author and the illustrator!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I ask him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe the dream team will reunite!
