Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka, what are you doing in a sweatsuit? What happened to the Manga Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I got away from my shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was the same person! We found out his name too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kugayama Muneyoshi! It was a real surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he someone famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
